Package: IntegratedLearner
Type: Package
Title: Integrated Multi-Omics Learner for Survival and Non-Survival Outcomes
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Himel", "Mallick", email = "nalina@example.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: IntegratedLearner provides a unified interface for multi-omics
    prediction using early, late, and intermediate fusion for continuous,
    binary, and survival outcomes. It wraps SuperLearner for non-survival
    tasks and a BioC-friendly native survival backend (no mlr3 dependency)
    for time-to-event modeling, handling both MultiAssayExperiment and PCL
    inputs with automated validation and feature alignment across layers.
